Here is a figure made of a circle inscribed in a square.
  5.00ft


  If the radius of the circle is 5.00 ft:
  


  (a) What is the area of the square?     \displaystyle{f}{t}^{{2}}
  


  (b) What is the area of the circle? Round to the nearest tenth.     \displaystyle{f}{t}^{{2}}
  


  (c) What is the area of the shaded section?     \displaystyle{f}{t}^{{2}}
